nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE NOW A POST-TROPICAL CYCLONE... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY...
summary: ...HENRIETTE NOW A POST-TROPICAL CYCLONE... ...THIS IS THE LAST ADVISORY... As of 11:00 PM HST Tue Aug 12 the center of Henriette was located near 36.7, -165.6 with movement NW at 20 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1008 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
